OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRather
OL,6,Fcloudy with a few showery outbreaks of
OL,7,Frain in the evening. Through the rest
OL,8,Fof the night cloudy conditions will
OL,9,Fcontinue with further showers at times.
OL,10,
OL,11,CMonday:FMainly cloudy in the morning
OL,12,Fwith showery outbreaks of rain.
OL,13,FTurning brighter but with a risk of
OL,14,Ffurther showers for a time in the
OL,15,Fafternoon.
