OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FDry
OL,6,Fand settled conditions prevail through
OL,7,Fthis period with light winds. Patchy
OL,8,Fcloud develops on Tuesday, before
OL,9,Fplenty of sunshine is expected on
OL,10,FWednesday and Thursday.
